    83‚Üíclass PluginManager:
    84‚Üí    """Core class which manages registration of plugin objects and 1:N hook
    85‚Üí    calling.
    86‚Üí
    87‚Üí    You can register new hooks by calling :meth:`add_hookspecs(module_or_class)
    88‚Üí    <PluginManager.add_hookspecs>`.
    89‚Üí
    90‚Üí    You can register plugin objects (which contain hook implementations) by
    91‚Üí    calling :meth:`register(plugin) <PluginManager.register>`.
    92‚Üí
    93‚Üí    For debugging purposes you can call :meth:`PluginManager.enable_tracing`
    94‚Üí    which will subsequently send debug information to the trace helper.
    95‚Üí
    96‚Üí    :param project_name:
    97‚Üí        The short project name. Prefer snake case. Make sure it's unique!
    98‚Üí    """
    99‚Üí

